data.description: Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the warm and inviting atmosphere of the home's well-thought-out layout. This home features three generously sized bedrooms, each offering ample space and natural light. The addition of a primary bedroom on the main level, complete with a convenient half bath, adds an extra layer of convenience and luxury to the living experience.This home is designed for modern living, with the first-floor laundry facilities making daily chores a breeze. A newer roof and furnace provide peace of mind and energy efficiency for years to come, ensuring your home is as comfortable as it is stylish.  The heart of the home, the kitchen, has been thoughtfully updated with granite countertops and new stainless steel appliances. Whether you're a seasoned chef or simply enjoy cooking for loved ones, this kitchen will delight you with its modern amenities and timeless appeal.  Cherry wood floors grace the living and dining areas, adding a touch of elegance and warmth to the space. These rooms are perfect for both everyday living and entertaining guests, with an open and welcoming atmosphere. The property sits on a 40x115 lot, which includes a fantastic side yard, providing plenty of space for outdoor enjoyment and recreational activities. Additionally, there is ample room to build an oversized garage, making this home even more versatile and practical for those with specific storage or workspace needs. This Expanded Cape Cod home near Midway Airport offers a combination of comfort, modern amenities, and the potential for personalization. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own and enjoy the convenience and style it has to offer. Come and explore this delightful property and envision the wonderful lifestyle it can provide for you and your family.
